value.0: I... Am Falcon. Guardian Spirit of the Silver Fangs, a hunter, nothing escapes my golden eye. Those who follow me should learn to become fast, strong, and stilled in battles.
I... Am Falcon. Guardian Spirit of the Silver Fangs, a hunter, nothing escapes my golden eye. Those who follow me should learn to become fast, strong, and stilled in battles.
I can tell you that I... am one of the oldest spirits, second only to but a few.
Yet I more than anyother  spirit have grown to hate the Wyrm most of all. For it was the Wyrm that enslaved many of my brood for many ages before this one.
We are... Those who are under me are some of Gaia's most fierce protectors.
I can teach you the first gift of the tribe.. But it does not come with out cost.
All gifts you learn from the spirits will cost you spirit energy. Gnosis. But others could require you be a certain rank, or to bring the spirit an offering... Criminage...
Then the Knowledge shall be inparted to you Young Claith.
I can teach you the second gift of the tribe.. But as before it does not come with out cost.
Bring to me the heart of one who is rarely tainted ... the Gurahl... Then I shall teach you.
Then the Knowledge shall be inparted to you young warrior.
